{"tid":1943145,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（突發）五區冇初選，但有民間民調投票","createTime":"2020-03-25T13:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T18:14:32.000Z","uid":324193,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0ee991244998351aaf94ddb8b200876a106a374e","tid":1943145,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:10:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200317/L74WMYCS2OC7AW7SMEEDDQVCAQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200317%2FL74WMYCS2OC7AW7SMEEDDQVCAQ%2F&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4VmNgp3wQ%2BT5fJEe%2BG4C8OY%3D&h=ae7468bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200317%2FL74WMYCS2OC7AW7SMEEDDQVCAQ%2F&h=e7e8f30a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200317/L74WMYCS2OC7AW7SMEEDDQVCAQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n九東有人搞選前初選，只會有投票日前兩日嘅民調+棄保機制，但咁樣不能減少參選名單，最終都會浪費選票<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200325/S2ABFQTHSPPXOCHFTAFGFJ36MY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200325%2FS2ABFQTHSPPXOCHFTAFGFJ36MY%2F&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4VmNgp3wQ%2BT5fJEe%2BG4C8OY%3D&h=ab2595bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200325%2FS2ABFQTHSPPXOCHFTAFGFJ36MY%2F&h=2a464fd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200325/S2ABFQTHSPPXOCHFTAFGFJ36MY/</a><br />\n<br />\n經過幾日俾壓力，九西就同意有初選+棄選機制，這是一個好開始，但九東就未有update 接納初選+棄選<br />\n<br />\n35+ 係全港選民共同目標，吾理你係泛民自決定本土，攞唔到過半都係冇意思<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n所以如果冇人搞初選，不如我地自己搞民間民調，支持度係0-1% 果啲吾該你考慮吓勝算+合組名單嘅可能<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n暫時未諗到點做民調，歡迎討論 <br />\n<br />\n但依家希望大家聯署要求左做初選先<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/ZgA6UiEXDMW43x3A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FZgA6UiEXDMW43x3A9&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4VmNgp3wQ%2BT5fJEe%2BG4C8OY%3D&h=b8bbbb6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/ZgA6UiEXDMW43x3A9</a><br />\n<br />\n另外，都想大家提討其他初選機制嘅公平性<br />\n<br />\n整左個表同數據，用區議員提名做初選/直選就最公平<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1942682\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1942682</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不了<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"43ec67100696b5d1b17c2768de6c866d79248a9d","tid":1943145,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:18:49.000Z","msg":"自推 1"},{"pid":"d1d3c2eaa40ca0bf9ff589488e63db2569fa9efc","tid":1943145,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:24:46.000Z","msg":"自推 2"},{"pid":"fbef64136838fabd00f7d150be3f6c9a63f8ed73","tid":1943145,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:34:31.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"0611b9442267ed8199acad9b939e0ae2be2d0402","tid":1943145,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:54:07.000Z","msg":"自推 4"},{"pid":"ec3ad1718b27f089cf8495f6b8618817ec7263b5","tid":1943145,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T14:32:34.000Z","msg":"自推 5"},{"pid":"f03651b144d04376af876113fcf6e6e1ec5f0bd4","tid":1943145,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T15:02:59.000Z","msg":"自推6"},{"pid":"fd34dbadb4f9b87f141750a9ded18f86e8883545","tid":1943145,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T06:58:34.000Z","msg":"自推7"},{"pid":"ccf8d275d901403f6d9f3038867f447def86457f","tid":1943145,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:54:05.000Z","msg":"【立會要初選 「三不投」聯署】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1945850\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1945850</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xSNcOdJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxSNcOdJ.png&h=83528c7d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b7a949bf60ed8ecc1eaddcbe64c2e271542cfac","tid":1943145,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T18:14:32.000Z","msg":"同意"}]}